ivardefs.name: authority
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the authority who published the protocol.  For example, ACIP.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: Contains the description about the protocol under which the vaccine was administered.

ivardefs.name: doseSequence
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the nominal position in a series of the next dose.  This is the recommended dose number as per a specified protocol.

ivardefs.name: series
ivardefs.desc: One possible path to achieve presumed immunity against a disease - within the context of an authority.

properties.desc: Contains information about the protocol under which the vaccine was administered.
